commit message:
Take more care not to make a jstring out of uninitialised custom config parts (#218)

Specifically, Unruly has a boolean with unset sval.
Fix #223: tell me what the user was playing at. :-)
Split startPlayingInt a bit. Crashes pointing there are inscrutable otherwise.

For #63, rule out Canvas state by making a new one when resizing.

One user already found this didn't help though. :-(

For #63, use ARGB_4444 on 4.1. Awaiting user feedback to confirm.

http://stackoverflow.com/questions/25921458/skewed-images-in-imageview-on-android-4-1-2
Fix undo/redo animation & keyboard control; remove some duplication. (#197)
Enable Proguard (with no obfuscation); bump version.

Merge from Simon's new official git repository.

This is 'merge -s ours', simply declaring a merge point with the new
version of the last relevant SVN change.

There are also  'git replace' mappings to replace git-svn history,
but they are *not* fetched by default and you will need to do this
if you want history to look nice:

git fetch origin 'refs/replace/*:refs/replace/*'
Add a notice to README about git replace.
Studio wants to git rm these; let it (fixes #140).

Automatic date-based version name, now Simon's using git.

Will automate version code somehow at some future time...
